    <item>
      <title>随着中国交易陷入停滞，菲律宾将目光投向其他石油资源丰富的地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/philippines-eyeing-other-oil-rich-areas-as-china-deal-stalled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位能源官员表示，菲律宾正在努力勘探该国其他可能蕴藏丰富石油和天然气的地区，因为两国之间的紧张关系导致与北京就南海联合资源开发的谈判陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/philippines-eyeing-other-oil-rich-areas-as-china-deal-stalled</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 07:19:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行拒绝降息后刺激支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/thailand-ramps-up-state-spending-after-pm-s-rate-cut-push-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着泰国央行拒绝紧急降息的呼吁，泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛正在采取措施增加国家支出和公共投资，以支撑东南亚第二大经济体的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/thailand-ramps-up-state-spending-after-pm-s-rate-cut-push-fails</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:10:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国机构警告气候措施可能引发社会动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/climate-measures-risk-sparking-social-unrest-german-agency-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国环境局局长表示，除非政界人士采取更多措施减轻碳价格上涨对低收入家庭的影响，否则欧盟的气候议程将面临广泛抵制的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/climate-measures-risk-sparking-social-unrest-german-agency-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国警方在基里巴斯报告后美国向太平洋发出警报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-alerts-pacific-after-report-of-chinese-police-in-kiribati</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有报道称中国警察正在夏威夷西南部小岛基里巴斯工作后，美国警告太平洋国家不要从中国“进口”安全部队，以帮助维护国内法律和秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-alerts-pacific-after-report-of-chinese-police-in-kiribati</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 05:45:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
