    <item>
      <title>马科斯确定菲律宾有争议的公投日期为 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/marcos-eyeing-2025-plebiscite-to-amend-philippine-constitution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，明年中期选举时可能会举行修宪公投，这推动了他修改宪法的计划，这一计划引发了该国最有权势的政治人物之间的激烈争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/marcos-eyeing-2025-plebiscite-to-amend-philippine-constitution</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:31:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登、特朗普在密歇根州获胜，距离 2024 年复赛越来越近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/biden-wins-michigan-primary-amid-uncommitted-vote-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登和共和党领跑者唐纳德·特朗普周二在密歇根州初选中双双获胜，两位候选人的结果表明民主党和共和党对可能的提名人都表示不满。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/biden-wins-michigan-primary-amid-uncommitted-vote-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:03:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国采取措施惩罚五名罢工医生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/south-korea-takes-legal-step-to-punish-five-doctors-for-walkout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国对五名涉嫌鼓励实习医生大规模罢工的医生提起刑事诉讼，采取了可能导致参加劳工行动的人员被吊销医疗执照的第一个法律步骤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/south-korea-takes-legal-step-to-punish-five-doctors-for-walkout</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 01:16:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国打击也门230个目标以回应红海袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/us-has-hit-230-targets-in-yemen-in-response-to-red-sea-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼一名高级官员表示，在胡塞武装领导的红海航运袭击事件之后，美国已经袭击了也门的 230 个目标，并提供了迄今为止最详细的空袭公开记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/us-has-hit-230-targets-in-yemen-in-response-to-red-sea-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:58:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国芯片制造商在美国商业秘密刑事案件中获得洗清</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/chinese-chipmaker-cleared-in-us-criminal-trade-secrets-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家中国芯片制造商被洗清了经济间谍罪和其他刑事指控，这让美国司法部打击中国盗窃知识产权的行动遭遇挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/chinese-chipmaker-cleared-in-us-criminal-trade-secrets-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:37:03 GMT</pubDate>
